York. I have to finish school.

32:06.754 --> 32:08.755
Why can't you do that in New York?

32:08.790 --> 32:10.824
They've got, like,
bunches of schools there.

32:10.859 --> 32:12.860
You know it's a myth that long distance

32:12.894 --> 32:16.029
