before computers and cell phones and...

32:16.064 --> 32:18.031
- You can make it work.
- Look guys,

32:18.066 --> 32:20.868
I don't want you to be
surprised, like Omar.

32:20.902 --> 32:25.973
I mean, we had a perfectly
nice night last night and, uh...

32:27.709 --> 32:28.675
then,

32:30.678 --> 32:32.679
I knew when I got up
this morning, I just...

32:34.849 --> 32:35.816
