hurting people around you.

35:07.635 --> 35:10.003
And then, maybe someone can love you.

35:18.946 --> 35:20.714
Sorry.

35:20.748 --> 35:21.882
Hi. Again.

35:24.585 --> 35:26.853
Look Clementine, about that letter...

35:26.888 --> 35:29.790
