lifetime to get over it.

35:54.882 --> 35:57.851
And I'll be satisfied just
being the best dad I can be.

35:57.885 --> 36:00.554
So, friends?

36:00.922 --> 36:01.888
Yeah.

36:12.633 --> 36:13.667
So...

36:14.702 --> 36:15.735
