37:31.294 --> 37:35.196
Come on man, I need some advice
here and I can't talk to my mom

37:35.231 --> 37:36.998
and dad because I don't
think they like Grace.

37:37.033 --> 37:38.133
- Why not?
- I don't think they've

37:38.167 --> 37:40.001
